                            <lb ed="I" n="0111a19"/>
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111a20"/>開二佛光明主洛州從事李<note n="0111001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30697;＝豹【中研院】</note><app n="0111001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">豹</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30697;</rdg></app>
