                    </div2>
                    <div2> 
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b01"/>大魏興和四<note n="0111002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30618;＝年【中研院】</note><app n="0111002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">年</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30618;</rdg></app>歲次降婁十月甲午<note n="0111003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30458;＝朔【中研院】</note><app n="0111003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">朔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30458;</rdg></app>八日辛丑。李氏合邑造□像碑頌文。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b02"/>夫<note n="0111004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB08073;＝旨【中研院】</note><app n="0111004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">旨</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB08073;</rdg></app>理虛沖。妙絕於言像之外。凝<note n="0111005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30699;＝湛【中研院】</note><app n="0111005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">湛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30699;</rdg></app><note n="0111006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30700;＝澹【中研院】</note><app n="0111006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">澹</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30700;</rdg></app>泊。超出於<note n="0111007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30701;＝無【中研院】</note><app n="0111007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">無</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30701;</rdg></app><note n="0111008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30702;＝形【中研院】</note><app n="0111008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">形</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30702;</rdg></app>之境。所以現應<note n="0111009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30645;＝金【中研院】</note><app n="0111009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">金</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30645;</rdg></app>容。<note n="0111010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30304;＝詮【中研院】</note><app n="0111010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">詮</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30304;</rdg></app>言<note n="0111011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30703;＝布【中研院】</note><app n="0111011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">布</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30703;</rdg></app>教者。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b03"/>寔由見聞之徒。三千同感。是以大<note n="0111012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30718;＝聖【中研院】</note><app n="0111012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">聖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30718;</rdg></app>降鑒。慈情&CB30698;接。影赴塵羈。悲拔<note n="0111013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02117;＝昏【中研院】</note><app n="0111013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">昏</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02117;</rdg></app>識。故能託&CB00528;淨王。 
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b04"/>搶現元吉。開三為級小之心。演一為接大之則。虛心<note n="0111014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30705;＝冥【中研院】</note><app n="0111014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">冥</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30705;</rdg></app>照。理<note n="0111015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30701;＝無【中研院】</note><app n="0111015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">無</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30701;</rdg></app>不統。深是如來處<note n="0111016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30706;＝有【中研院】</note><app n="0111016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">有</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30706;</rdg></app>不<note n="0111017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30706;＝有【中研院】</note><app n="0111017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">有</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30706;</rdg></app>。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b05"/>居<note n="0111018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30701;＝無【中研院】</note><app n="0111018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">無</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30701;</rdg></app>不<note n="0111019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30701;＝無【中研院】</note><app n="0111019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">無</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30701;</rdg></app>者<note n="0111020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30707;＝矣【中研院】</note><app n="0111020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">矣</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30707;</rdg></app>。但以眾生福盡。不<note n="0111021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB13224;＝善【中研院】</note><app n="0111021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">善</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB13224;</rdg></app>諸業。百八雲張。<note n="0111022" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">耶＝邪【中研院】</note><app n="0111022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">邪</lem><rdg wit="【原】">耶</rdg></app>風競扇。致令靈曜潛暉。遷感異域。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b06"/>自<note n="0111023" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30718;＝聖【中研院】</note><app n="0111023"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">聖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30718;</rdg></app>去遙延。世華道<note n="0111024" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB07656;＝喪【中研院】</note><app n="0111024"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">喪</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB07656;</rdg></app>。然今季末李次。李顯族百餘人。藉冑軒皇。蘭枝玉葉。望美<note n="0111025" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB13426;＝海【中研院】</note><app n="0111025"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">海</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB13426;</rdg></app>標。仁
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b07"/>英<note n="0111026" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30716;＝達【中研院】</note><app n="0111026"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">達</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30716;</rdg></app><note n="0111027" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30708;＝傑【中研院】</note><app n="0111027"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">傑</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30708;</rdg></app>。<note n="0111028" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30709;＝厥【中研院】</note><app n="0111028"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">厥</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30709;</rdg></app>祖乃宗出自趙壟。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">因</unclear>官爰處。即居<note n="0111029" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB01150;＝黎【中研院】</note><app n="0111029"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">黎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB01150;</rdg></app>境。乘此敷分。胤隆千室。雖<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">寄</unclear>異方。抱馨轉
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b08"/>馥。子孫孤挺。夙姿天哲。跗萼相承。懸光槐<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">蕀</unclear>。復能顯揚大法。咸皆信敬。內□□隆三寶。故
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b09"/>勸我見。以識苦空。導迷徒以曉八正。情永獨<note n="0111030" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB13224;＝善【中研院】</note><app n="0111030"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">善</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB13224;</rdg></app>之非。<note n="0111031" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30710;＝思【中研院】</note><app n="0111031"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">思</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30710;</rdg></app>同物樂者耳。於是孰契齊心。同發
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b10"/>洪願。即於村中造寺一<note n="0111032" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00100;＝區【中研院】</note><app n="0111032"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">區</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00100;</rdg></app>。僧坊四周。講堂已就。建塔陵雲。靈圖岳峻。列彩星分。<note n="0111033" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30645;＝金【中研院】</note><app n="0111033"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">金</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30645;</rdg></app>光煥□。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b11"/>其時宇宙清夷。靜安皇祚。民豐世<note n="0111034" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30711;＝業【中研院】</note><app n="0111034"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">業</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30711;</rdg></app>。率誘相從。□<note n="0111035" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB13224;＝善【中研院】</note><app n="0111035"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">善</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB13224;</rdg></app>增歡。妙悟日益。競捨□□。重興勝福。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b12"/>復於村南二里。大河北<note n="0111036" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">圻＝岸【中研院】</note><app n="0111036"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">岸</lem><rdg wit="【原】">圻</rdg></app>。万路交過。水陸俱要。滄<note n="0111037" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB13426;＝海【中研院】</note><app n="0111037"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">海</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB13426;</rdg></app>之賓攸攸。伊洛之客亦屆。逕春溫之
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b13"/>苦渴。涉夏暑之炎<note n="0111038" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30730;＝燠【中研院】</note><app n="0111038"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">燠</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30730;</rdg></app>。愍茲行流。故於路傍造石<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">井</unclear>一口。種樹兩十根。以息渴乏。由斯建立。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b14"/>遐途稱<note n="0111039" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB13224;＝善【中研院】</note><app n="0111039"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">善</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB13224;</rdg></app>。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">因</unclear>前生<note n="0111040" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30713;＝復【中研院】</note><app n="0111040"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">復</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30713;</rdg></app>。信心□著。重福輕珍。復竭家玩。次造天宮浮圖四<note n="0111041" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00100;＝區【中研院】</note><app n="0111041"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">區</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00100;</rdg></app>。交龍石碑像一
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b15"/>軀。訪匠妙盡於寰中。召能募出於宇內。靈姿赫弈。<note n="0111042" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30717;＝若【中研院】</note><app n="0111042"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">若</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30717;</rdg></app><note n="0111043" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30645;＝金【中研院】</note><app n="0111043"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">金</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30645;</rdg></app>山之□朗。<note n="0111044" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30703;＝布【中研院】</note><app n="0111044"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">布</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30703;</rdg></app>彩煙霄。雲張字列。圖
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b16"/>飾嚴麗。暉明照灼。鏤玉剋<note n="0111045" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30645;＝金【中研院】</note><app n="0111045"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">金</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30645;</rdg></app>。眾寶廁瑱。論妙拔歎所不能窮。語相好思所不能及。巍巍焉
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b17"/><note n="0111046" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30717;＝若【中研院】</note><app n="0111046"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">若</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30717;</rdg></app>須<note n="0111047" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB12752;＝彌【中研院】</note><app n="0111047"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB12752;</rdg></app>之顯海。堂棠乎有相而難名。成因感果。須達未足為殊。得報獲益。祇阤豈曰非譬。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b18"/>古者尚存名竹帛。況今焉不<note n="0111048" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30706;＝有【中研院】</note><app n="0111048"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">有</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30706;</rdg></app>流述者耳。故刊石記功。聲傳後代。而作頌曰。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b19"/>寂寂虛沖。眇漠難名。赴感隨緣。應物以<note n="0111049" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30702;＝形【中研院】</note><app n="0111049"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">形</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30702;</rdg></app>。虛通縱任。王□託生。振威雷動。六合欹傾。魔道
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b20"/>歸降。亡魂<note n="0111050" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30692;＝喪【中研院】</note><app n="0111050"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">喪</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30692;</rdg></app>精。圓音報万。正法暉明。暉明照世。緣盡喪逝。堂堂妙身。遷感以波。娑羅北首。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b21"/>聲光唱滅。大眾哀請。三業燋裂。不果所願。徒流灑血。嗚呼慈父。追號難逮。難逮叵追。分留
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b22"/>異處。念念遷謝。<note n="0111051" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30394;＝彌【中研院】</note><app n="0111051"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30394;</rdg></app><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">傷</unclear><note n="0111052" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30718;＝聖【中研院】</note><app n="0111052"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">聖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30718;</rdg></app>去。<note n="0111053" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30701;＝無【中研院】</note><app n="0111053"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">無</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30701;</rdg></app>主<note n="0111054" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30701;＝無【中研院】</note><app n="0111054"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">無</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30701;</rdg></app>親。眾生戀慕。憶想<note n="0111055" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30645;＝金【中研院】</note><app n="0111055"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">金</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30645;</rdg></app>顏。剋彫飾素。匠玉鏤&CB00216;。表容感悟。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b23"/>斯等邑人。置立方處。方處臨河。據村南東。平原顯<note n="0111056" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30714;＝敞【中研院】</note><app n="0111056"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">敞</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30714;</rdg></app>。行路過逢。人瞻<note n="0111057" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30719;＝歸【中研院】</note><app n="0111057"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">歸</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30719;</rdg></app>仰。府□虔恭。唅詠 
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b24"/>發心。報福<note n="0111058" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30705;＝冥【中研院】</note><app n="0111058"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">冥</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30705;</rdg></app>鍾。<note n="0111059" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30705;＝冥【中研院】</note><app n="0111059"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">冥</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30705;</rdg></app>鍾之福。願如<note n="0111060" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30645;＝金【中研院】</note><app n="0111060"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">金</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30645;</rdg></app><note n="0111061" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30369;＝剛【中研院】</note><app n="0111061"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">剛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30369;</rdg></app>。當使皇祚晏安。寧靜邊方。合邑慶賴。耆幼<note n="0111062" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">烋＝休【中研院】</note><app n="0111062"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">休</lem><rdg wit="【原】">烋</rdg></app>昌。逮及
                            <lb ed="I" n="0111b25"/>七世。現在存亡。潤兼法界。同生安養。　　　　　　　　都邑金像義井主長樂太守李次　金像主李逵
